These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, tea
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, peach, plum, radish
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, gardening, puzzles, writing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, october, february, june
4 different pets are kept: turtle, snake, goldfish, cat
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, satire, disaster, adventure
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is the owner of the turtle##1
 3. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 4. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 5. the person drinking tea is the person eating radish##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person watching time-travel movies and the owner of the cat##2
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
10. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person eating radish##2
11. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
12. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who's hobby is writing##1
13. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the snake and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | tea        | coffee       | lemonade  | almond-milk |
| Food          | radish     | plum         | peach     | broccoli    |
| Hobby         | gardening  | fishing      | puzzles   | writing     |
| Birthday           | october | april | february   | june     |
| Pet   | snake    | goldfish         | turtle | cat         |
| Movie-Genre         | adventure     | time-travel     | satire  | disaster       |

