.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, azure, lilac, green
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, filmmaking, skydiving, writing
4 different pets are kept: horse, dog, goat, rabbit
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, golf, water-polo
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, german, malaysian, pakistani
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, ship, train
 1. the german is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person driving the bike##2
 2. the pakistani is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the canadian##1
 4. the german is between the person who likes ebony and the person driving the ship##2
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who likes azure##1
 6. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the owner of the horse and the person who's hobby is writing##2
 9. the owner of the dog is the person who's hobby is writing##1
10. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1
11. the person who's sport is baseball is the owner of the goat##1
12. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
13. the malaysian is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
14. the person who likes azure is on the left of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Color      | green    | azure       | lilac   | ebony |
| Hobby         | chess     | skydiving   | writing    | filmmaking  |
| Pet   | horse    | goat | dog   | rabbit     |
