The people have 4 different hobbies: horsed-games, collecting, gardening, reading
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, designer, scientist, software-developer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, family, scientific
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, surfing, golf, parkour
4 different pets are kept: horse, ferret, pony, turtle
 1. the person playing canasta is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's sport is golf##2
 2. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the designer##1
 3. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 4. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 6. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 7. the scientist is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 8. the owner of the pony is the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the owner of the horse is between the scientist and the person who's hobby is horsed-games##2
10. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is horsed-games is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
12. the software-developer is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
13. the person playing backgammon is the person playing backgammon##1
14. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |         2          |     3      |     4     |
